For admins:

Q:  How to bootstrap a new Ubuntu 16.04 server in our cluster?

    1.  log in as a user that has sudo permission

    2.  download the bootstrap script

            wget https://fast-crypto-lab.github.io/cluster/bootstrap

    3.  run the bootstrap script

            sudo bash bootstrap

Q:  How to generate fcl.json, ssh_config, and ssh_known_hosts?

    1.  update the content of cluster-info/hosts/ and cluster-info/users/

    2.  run the compile script

            ./compile

    3.  check the resulting fcl.json, ssh_config, and ssh_known_hosts files
